[b]1.Welcome.[/b] [i]Welcome to project pimp! The idea of this project is to, well, redesign pimpscape source! Im not sure if I'm going to host it yet, i might just realse. Anyway, im going to add alot more stuff in which some newbies might not be able to do. So really, im making a very nice and easy starting source. Im hoping to take some KB of the client class with some handlers. Also, using xero's anti-lag, lag will reduce 50%+ So you will be able to get more players![/i]
[hr]
[b]2.Known delays.[/b] [i]Here are the known delays of coding.[/i]
[ul][li][b]21th of October - Im going bowling today, there will be some coding done tho.[/b][/li] [li][b]22nd of October - My birthday.[/b][/li] [li][b]23rd of October - Be playing my new game - Will do some coding tho.[/b][/li] [li][b]--UPCOMING--[/b][/li] [li][b]--UPCOMING--[/b][/li] [li][b]--UPCOMING--[/b][/li] [li][b]--UPCOMING--[/b][/li][/ul]
